rogressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3029a450-6d3e-4d43-a5e5-65d4e98302f5_920x584.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3029a450-6d3e-4d43-a5e5-65d4e98302f5_920x584.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3029a450-6d3e-4d43-a5e5-65d4e98302f5_920x584.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3029a450-6d3e-4d43-a5e5-65d4e98302f5_920x584.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></figure></div><p>今天，我想对一场技术革命进行大声疾呼。</p><p>我写了很多关于<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/decade-of-the-battery-334">电池崛起</a>，<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/at-least-five-interesting-things-84f">绿色能源的胜利</a>以及在2020年代发生的其他<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/techno-optimism-for-2024">技术革命的</a>文章。但是这些发展中的许多是相关的。我认为它们是如此深刻而根本的转变的可见突出，几乎很难描述它。这是关于整个人类技术的基本物理过程的转变。</p><p>我记得我十几岁的时候，与我的朋友一起观看卡通表演<a href="https://gizmodo.com/why-robotech-is-the-greatest-love-story-of-the-20th-cen-5971053">Robotech</a> （最初发行后很多年；我不<em>那么</em>老！）。在节目中，有一个名为“原始培养”的秘密超强能源。我记得我的一个朋友问：“您如何从原始文化中获得能量？另一个朋友说：“好吧，首先，您使用原始培养将水烧成蒸汽，然后用它来转动涡轮机……”</p><p>我们都笑了，但是这个笑话源于技术现实。直到今天，大多数电源（包括核能）基本上只是<em>加热水</em>，这将其变成蒸汽，这推动了某种轮子，a）变成了使机器运行的一些齿轮，或者b）产生电流的磁铁。对于化石燃料电源（尽管不是用于核能），这涉及<em>燃烧</em>- 从化学反应中迅速释放热量。</p><p>燃烧是人类提取和运输能量的两种主要方法之一。了解如何利用燃烧可能是人类历史上最重要的技术革命。由煤炭动力蒸汽机以及油驱动的内燃机提供的能源，允许创建机械化农业，现代制造，铁路运输，汽车，卡车，现代运输，动力飞行以及大多数东西这使人类从我们开始的贫困贫困之泥中升起。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42571286-a0a4-4cfd-9c3d-e5361f51f668_1020x725.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42571286-a0a4-4cfd-9c3d-e5361f51f668_1020x725.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42571286-a0a4-4cfd-9c3d-e5361f51f668_1020x725.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42571286-a0a4-4cfd-9c3d-e5361f51f668_1020x725.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42571286-a0a4-4cfd-9c3d-e5361f51f668_1020x725.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42571286-a0a4-4cfd-9c3d-e5361f51f668_1020x725.jpeg" width="652" height="463.4313725490196" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/42571286-a0a4-4cfd-9c3d-e5361f51f668_1020x725.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:725,&quot;width&quot;:1020,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:652,&quot;bytes&quot;:107796,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42571286-a0a4-4cfd-9c3d-e5361f51f668_1020x725.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42571286-a0a4-4cfd-9c3d-e5361f51f668_1020x725.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42571286-a0a4-4cfd-9c3d-e5361f51f668_1020x725.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42571286-a0a4-4cfd-9c3d-e5361f51f668_1020x725.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>但是，第二次技术革命正在进行中，这也改变了我们世界的面貌。这是<em>电</em>- 通过导电材料移动电子的能力。</p><p>电力和燃烧是互补的 - 例如，当您燃烧煤炭以将水烧开以将涡轮机燃烧以转动产生电力的发电机时。当然，两者都依靠某种形式的化学势能（一个汽油箱，电池等）来运输存储的能量。</p><p><a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-triumph-of-electromagnetism-over">阅读更多</a></p>; 
